Possible categories: MASTER, MUSIC, RECORDS, WEATHER, BLOCKS, HOSTILE, NEUTRAL, PLAYERS, AMBIENT, or VOICE.

Plays a sound at the given location. SoundArray is in an associative array with keys 'sound', 'category', 'volume', 'pitch', where all are optional except sound. Volume, if greater than 1.0 (default), is the distance in chunks players can hear the sound. Pitch has a range of 0.5 - 2.0, where where 1.0 is the middle pitch and default. Players can be a single player or an array of players to play the sound to, if not given, all players can potentially hear it.
